Evolution Redirect Plugin

Description:
This plugin is used for when creating a new website in MODX Evolution where client had an old site and we want to redirect the old site pages to new resources on the new site.

To Install:
* Create a new plugin:
* Name:
  Redirects
* Description:
  <strong>0.0.4</strong> Redirects old URL's to the new ones
* Paste in plugin code
* Edit $sites array with your old pages and docid to redirect to
* On system events tab select OnPageNotFound